Common.LongDescription.Common.Text:
A major northern industrial holding of 3.5 Ha approx located on a corner site (Hawker & Diment Roads) in Burton.

The property is in the process of being sub-divided into six 5,000 sq m and one 4,690 sq m parcels, but is available as a whole or in individual allotments within the afore-mentioned ranges.

Land bank, develop or owner occupy.

The property is zoned Industry in the City of Salisbury.

The land is regular in shape, with frontage to Diment Road of 115 metres approx and Hawker Road of well over 280 metres approx.

For sale via Expressions of Interest closing Thursday 10th July at 4:00 pm.
